      "content": "everything is just so much right now. i feel like i cant even go outside without thinking about what people are saying about me online. it feels like everyone has already decided i'm a bad person and there's no way to change it. i just feel so alone and exhausted. i dont even know why i bother waking up every day if it's just gonna be more of this.",
